reviews.review_text: Great AUD, Better Show AUD's from Red Rocks are usually iffy at best, but this one is outstanding.  Clear and crisp with Phil especially coming through loud and clear.  This run at RR was some great stuff, with Jerry on top of his game and full of energy.  This show is fine example with some great renditions of Shakedown, Big River and, yes, even Hell In A Bucket in the 1st set.  But the real magic is in the 2nd set. The Scarlet>Fire alone gets a 5 Star in my book.  Just out-freakin'-standing.  Jerry is on fire (no pun intended).  Great, great stuff here in great quality.  Will not dissapoint.
